SCC Requirements:

Windows:
   Microsoft Visual C++ 2008 SP1 Redistributable Package (x86)
   http://www.microsoft.com/download/en/details.aspx?displaylang=en&id=5582

Linux Debian/Ubuntu packages:
   libssl-dev libqca2-dev libqca2-plugin-ossl libphonon-dev g++ cmake make

If you want to use "cmake" with custom options, type:

   cmake . [options]
   make
   make install

On Windows "make install" does not fully work. Edit cmake options in compile.bat instead.

Available options:

   -DWITH_KAMERZYSTA=OFF 
      to compile without Kamerzysta connection (default OFF on Unix/Linux)

   -DWITH_PHONON=OFF
      to compile without Phonon

   -DWIN32_QCA2_DIR=DIR
      to compile with non-standard libQCA path i.e.: -DWIN32_QCA2_DIR=C:\QCA2

   -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug
      to compile with full debug
